name: Jokey Yokey - Farm Barn Circus confetti eggs 5 DZN
description:
discover more at: www.JokeyYokey.com

In my effort to spread simple happiness, I offer to you Jokey Yokey confetti eggs. Inspired by Latin American tradition of the Cascarones – a confetti filled eggshell cracked over ones head to bring good luck and cheer – and my family’s ability to discover the simple pleasures, Jokey Yokey confetti eggs were created to remind you that life is fun. 

These hand-crafted, clever confetti creations are made of repurposed egg shell, confetti and tissue paper - the glue and glitter are even homemade with natural ingredients. 100% biodegradable - Jokey Yokey confetti eggs are amusing adolescence and adults alike spreading their happiness beyond your celebration and onto our mother earth.

Now go, crack open the happy ;)

SPREADING THE CHEER! Jokey Yokey confetti eggs won't just put a smile on your face but spread their happiness on to those in need. Partnering with the Helping Up Mission of Baltimore, Jokey Yokey confetti eggs donates the "inners" of each egg to help feed the homeless. Now that's no joke!

This order contains 5 dozen confetti eggs of assorted primary blue, red, yellow and green, coordinating confetti and glitter. 

How many do you need? Rule of my thumb - 2-3 confetti eggs per person. Although, the more the merrier!

CUSTOM ORDERS AVAILABLE - just send me a message and we can create the Jokey Yokey confetti egg you desire!

WHOLESALE ORDERS AVAILABLE - send me a message to inquire. 

If these are for an event, please specify exact date you need them by during checkout. Please see my policies section for more on shipping times.

name: Jokey Yokey - A Spring Loaded Easter confetti eggs
description:
There's no better inspiration than desire
and the weather here at Jokey Yokey headquarters
is leaving alot to be desired.

This months Merriment is not inspired by the drab,
dreary and dread but rather
the rainbow after the rain, the sun behind the clouds
and the bloom inside the bud. 

Showcasing our own interpretation of ROY G. BIV
and the powerful idea of renewal,
Spring-Loaded Jokey Yokey confetti eggs will
burst open your happy and hatch your good cheer. 

So, rain, rain you can go, go away - there's a confetti egg over this head today!

To discover more go to www.JokeyYokey.com

Cheers & Happy Cracking!
Laurin
(smile maker)
